  "content": "<p data-pid=\"arzusZX2\">把复习作为一个挑战，不要被动地再去重新看一遍书，那个确实有点没意思，特别是你粗略看下来感觉自己都会，就更无聊且低效了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2e422c3ee8a2a3e75d6264910d6bd7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"403\" data-original-token=\"v2-fc4ffc57ff2983d4a3689e8c4ae8a61e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1485dbe889055494c6e5a16194420be1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7b2e422c3ee8a2a3e75d6264910d6bd7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;403&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"403\" data-original-token=\"v2-fc4ffc57ff2983d4a3689e8c4ae8a61e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1485dbe889055494c6e5a16194420be1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7b2e422c3ee8a2a3e75d6264910d6bd7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2e422c3ee8a2a3e75d6264910d6bd7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><h2><b>正确的方法是通过测试来复习</b></h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1569017d9fb876d0a432b1690ad2c919_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"404\" data-original-token=\"v2-40944ea928a1b255de63a5bff4ef0f87\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-890d187e171d120d6d4a12c16abe1d1e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1569017d9fb876d0a432b1690ad2c919_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;404&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"404\" data-original-token=\"v2-40944ea928a1b255de63a5bff4ef0f87\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-890d187e171d120d6d4a12c16abe1d1e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1569017d9fb876d0a432b1690ad2c919_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1569017d9fb876d0a432b1690ad2c919_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"KLKJH-nt\">当然，测试并不止与老师的随堂小测、周练、阶段性大考，其实测试可以伴随我们每一天，那就是自测。</p><p data-pid=\"8Xlbk-7M\">怎么每一天都能通过自测来复习呢？自己出题难度高，买来的卷子又不适合随时自测。那就考考自己有没有记住自己的笔记好了。</p><p data-pid=\"Zmua3JXc\">可是复习笔记的话，就需要把笔记写成问答或者填空的形式，这样做起来在纸质的笔记本上很不方便(虽然有康奈尔笔记法，不过我用不来)</p><p data-pid=\"LY9o3WxU\">那就靠电子设备来帮忙，我首推 <b>Anki </b>！</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d86e2359e71995ab01407f4981de7409_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-original-token=\"v2-451ff878834bb73f287c1010a1281c2d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-412fbc6aedbd684ea1d5e7aaa1bb94ee_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d86e2359e71995ab01407f4981de7409_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;540&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-original-token=\"v2-451ff878834bb73f287c1010a1281c2d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-412fbc6aedbd684ea1d5e7aaa1bb94ee_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d86e2359e71995ab01407f4981de7409_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d86e2359e71995ab01407f4981de7409_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>笔记卡片正面</figcaption></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4252a98b7da31fc69b16e0656434bc5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-original-token=\"v2-b305b67b6ede8d1a0eb552c880676d97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1ca56ab7d1378f1e2662a612faf273d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c4252a98b7da31fc69b16e0656434bc5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;540&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-original-token=\"v2-b305b67b6ede8d1a0eb552c880676d97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1ca56ab7d1378f1e2662a612faf273d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c4252a98b7da31fc69b16e0656434bc5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4252a98b7da31fc69b16e0656434bc5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>笔记卡片背面</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"DrDABX6L\">这是电脑版的，适合用于制作自己的笔记。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;634&#39; height=&#39;542&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"eBBaksLY\">这是手机版，适合平时复习。(不同按钮对应熟悉程度，时间表示算法安排的下一次复习时间)</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-acecd59a65c372b0022aee05e330d843_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1365\" data-rawheight=\"741\" data-original-token=\"v2-1097e9f4ac166a27aa53dcaa93e21abc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e790e6a76ba526d433f4016974a4ac77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1365\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-acecd59a65c372b0022aee05e330d843_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1365&#39; height=&#39;741&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1365\" data-rawheight=\"741\" data-original-token=\"v2-1097e9f4ac166a27aa53dcaa93e21abc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e790e6a76ba526d433f4016974a4ac77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1365\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-acecd59a65c372b0022aee05e330d843_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-acecd59a65c372b0022aee05e330d843_7